      <h1 class="big">Mission &amp; Vision</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
      <p>Our goal is to clearly communicate the message of hope and eternal salvation found only in <em>Jesus Christ</em>. This hope and eternal salvation is not found in religion or organization, but only in a living, personal and dynamic relationship with <em>Jesus Christ</em>.</p>
      <p>Our <u>mission</u> at NLCF is to know <em>Christ</em> and to make Him Known.<br>
      Our <u>vision</u> is transforming lives and impacting the world for <em>Jesus Christ</em> by becoming a spiritually functioning, divinely dependent, and praying Christian community.</p>
